By the way, it is using a random port, doing it programmatically, that is executed as a static method before the application bootstrap.
@BeforeAll
    public static void beforeAll() {
        BaseProcessTimerIT.beforeAll(() -> SocketUtils.findAvailableTcpPort());
        System.setProperty("server.port", String.valueOf(BaseProcessTimerIT.httpPort));
    }

